    <step order="3" name="Module placement decision + interface design">
      Decide module placement. Two candidates:

      - **Candidate A**: `src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/src/services/insightsQuery
        Client.ts` (alongside existing services like `notificationContextLoader.
        ts`). Pros: localized to the SpaarkeAi shell where the only consumer
        lives today; matches existing services folder convention. Cons:
        future Office Add-in reuse would require extraction.
      - **Candidate B**: `src/client/shared/Spaarke.AI.Insights.Client/src/
